about:

A long-time Memphis, TN, institution, Tommy Wright III's Street Smart Records developed a cult following in the South, with a dark, malevolent tone quite similar to Three Six Mafia but with a much grittier sound. Manson Family represents a small stable of rappers associated with Wright: K-Rocafella, C-Rocafella, C-9, Princess Loko, Lil' Sko, Mac T-Dog, and producer Maceo. Many of these rappers display remarkable skills, and Maceo's production proves evocative, with its horror film ambience and mid-tempo drum machine bounce.
